        "Description": "\u7406\u4E0D\u5C3D\u306B\u6012\u3089\u308C\u308B\u3053\u3068\u3063\u3066\u3042\u308B\u3088\r\n\u306A\u3002\u3060\u3051\u3069\u305D\u308C\u304C\u4EBA\u9593\u304B\u3089\u306A\u3089\u3001\r\n\u7121\u8996\u3057\u3066\u3084\u308C\u3070\u3044\u3044\u3002\u3060\u3051\u3069\u3001\r\n\u30E9\u30FC\u30B8\u30E3\u30F3\u304B\u3089\u306A\u3089\u8A71\u306F\u5225\u3060\u3002\r\n\u62E0\u70B9\u3060\u3063\u3066\u3076\u3063\u58CA\u3055\u308C\u3061\u307E\u3046\u3002\r\n\u983C\u3080\u305C\u3002\u3068\u3063\u3066\u304A\u304D\u306E\uFF11\u676F\u3001\r\n\u304A\u3054\u3089\u305B\u3066\u3082\u3089\u3046\u304B\u3089\u3088\u3002",
        "Target": "\u6FC0\u6602\u3057\u305F\u30E9\u30FC\u30B8\u30E3\u30F3\uFF11\u982D\u306E\u72E9\u731F",
        "Fail": "\u5831\u916C\u91D1\u30BC\u30ED\r\n\u30BF\u30A4\u30E0\u30A2\u30C3\u30D7"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Unreasonable Rage",
        "Client": "Fatalistic Barkeep",
        "Description": "We all get burned from time to\r\ntime... And if it\u0027s someone you\r\nlove doing it, you can just turn\r\nthe other cheek. But we\u0027re talkin\u0027\r\nabout a Rajang here. And if you\r\ndon\u0027t do something about it, all\r\nour cheeks are gonna get burned!",
        "Target": "Hunt a Furious Rajang",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Rage non justifi\u00E9e",
        "Client": "Tavernier fataliste",
        "Description": "\u00C7a arrive \u00E0 tout le monde de\r\nse faire mal de temps \u00E0 autre,\r\npas vrai ? Et si on nous fait\r\nmal, on passe outre, mais avec\r\nun Rajang, c\u0027est une autre\r\nhistoire. Il va tous nous\r\nd\u00E9truire si tu nous aides pas !",
        "Target": "Chasser un Rajang orage",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Furia irragionevole",
        "Client": "Gestore di bar fatalista",
        "Description": "Ogni tanto a tutti capita di\r\nvenire scottati ingiustamente,\r\nno? Se \u00E8 una persona a farlo,\r\nsi pu\u00F2 lasciar perdere, ma se\r\n\u00E8 un Rajang, allora \u00E8 tutta\r\nun\u0027altra storia. L\u0027intera base\r\nverr\u00E0 distrutta! Devi aiutarci!",
        "Target": "Caccia un Rajang furioso",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Ungeb\u00FChrliche Rage",
        "Client": "Fatalistischer Barkeeper",
        "Description": "Wir alle erleiden gelegentlich\r\nunfaire Niederlagen, oder?\r\nUnd manchmal kann man dar\u00FCber\r\nhinwegsehen. Aber hier haben\r\nwir es mit einem Rajang zu tun!\r\nWir m\u00FCssen was unternehmen,\r\nsonst macht er uns die H\u00F6lle hei\u00DF!",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Zornigen Rajang.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Locura desmedida",
        "Client": "Camarero pesimista",
        "Description": "Todos terminamos un poco quemados\r\nde vez en cuando, \u00BFno? Y si es por\r\nculpa de un ser querido, se puede\r\nperdonar... \u00A1pero en este caso es\r\nun Rajang! \u00A1Como no nos ayudes,\r\nno nos perdonar\u00E1 ni la vida!",
        "Target": "Caza un Rajang Rabioso",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u041D\u0435\u0441\u043F\u0440\u0430\u0432\u0435\u0434\u043B\u0438\u0432\u044B\u0439 \u0433\u043D\u0435\u0432",
        "Client": "\u0422\u0440\u0430\u043A\u0442\u0438\u0440\u0449\u0438\u043A-\u0444\u0430\u0442\u0430\u043B\u0438\u0441\u0442",
